These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: orange, garlic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, golf
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is not the person eating garlic##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | garlic   | orange  |
| Sport   | handball | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, strawberry
2 different pets are kept: dog, rabbit
1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the dog is not the person eating strawberry##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | lettuce | strawberry      |
| Pet    | dog  | rabbit |

 #################################

 
