.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, drama
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, ice-hockey
1. the person watching drama movies is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6
2. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | drama |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | weightlifting      |

