.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, soul
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, pakistani
1. the fan disco is on the far right##1
2. the fan soul is not the colombian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | disco      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | colombian |

