.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, freelancer
2 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit
1. the lawyer is in an odd position##4
2. the lawyer is not the owner of the rabbit##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | lawyer | freelancer |
| Pet   | snake       | rabbit       |

